  <Name>Scorching Ray</Name>
  <CastingTime>1 action</CastingTime>
  <Range>120 feet</Range>
  <Duration>Instantaneous</Duration>
  <Level>2</Level>
  <Description>You create three rays of fire and hurl them at targets within range. You can hurl them at one target or several.
Make a ranged spell attack for each ray. On a hit, the target takes 2d6 fire damage.</Description>
  <Descriptions>
    <Description>
      <Name>At Higher Levels</Name>
      <Text>When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 3rd level or higher, you create one additional ray for each slot level above 2nd.</Text>
    </Description>
  </Descriptions>
